    "accordion_content_NbwLxx": {
      "type": "accordion-content",
      "blocks": {
        "item_3xdhDL": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "DESIGN",
            "content": "<p>The Rito Trike is built to evolve with your child, offering a seamless transition through every stage of development. With multiple footrests and easily removable parts, it provides a perfect fit from 10 months to 36+ months, ensuring comfort, support, and lasting enjoyment.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_ML3giN": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "HOW TO ASSEMBLE",
            "content": "<p>Setting up your Rito Trike is simple! Follow along with our step-by-step assembly <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJTaCZwJHKs\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJTaCZwJHKs\"><em><strong>video guide </strong></em></a>to get your trike ready in no time. Watch now and have your little one riding in just a few minutes.</p>",
            "page": "bentley-trike-assembly"
          }
        },
        "item_zErg3p": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "SPARE PARTS",
            "content": "<p>Every journey deserves to be seamless. If any part of your Bentley Trike needs replacing, continue the experience by ordering an official Bentley spare part <a href=\"/pages/bentley-trike-assembly\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bentley Trike Assembly\">here</a>. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_keFK64": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "WARRANTY",
            "content": "<p>If you experience any issues with your Bentley Trike within the <strong>2-year warranty </strong>period, we’re here to ensure a seamless solution. Simply enter your details in the form below, and our team will assist you promptly.</p><p><em>Please note : Warranty coverage applies exclusively to purchases made directly from us. If purchased elsewhere, kindly reach out to the original retailer for assistance</em></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "item_3xdhDL",
        "item_ML3giN",
        "item_zErg3p",
        "item_keFK64"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "The Ultimate Folding Trike",
        "content": "<p>Rito is the ultimate 3-in-1 stroller/trike for kids and offers the best combination of portability, style, and functionality.</p><p>The Rito folds down for easy storage and transport, unlike most toddler trikes, making it easier for parents to carry the trike in cars, public transport, and even tricky terrains such as escalators.</p>",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_url": "",
        "text_position": "start",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": "",
